{"tid":734582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一有地就起樓","createTime":"2018-07-08T17:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T18:10:03.000Z","uid":13882,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e738c9f325cff74f35807e3ed3369497e2f70871","tid":734582,"uid":13882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T17:52:48.000Z","msg":"其實有地起樓係好<br />\n但係唔該唔好再係比d支那人住<br />\n比返我地香港市民住先係正路<br />\n就算係要用粉嶺個哥爾夫球場<br />\n我都覺得ok<br />\n(但事實上入面嘅路好窄，真係要發展嘅話，交通真係唔知應唔應付到)<br />\n最理想就係用石崗軍營發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依加問題係好多野都比支那人佔據哂<br />\n個個上電視講到自己幾慘<br />\n但其實根本可能係大陸有大屋住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋唔該廢老唔好再娶大陸婆落黎香港！<br />\n<br />\n利申:由細到大都住新界北區<br />\n一直覺得自己住咁鄉下地方應該安安靜靜<br />\n真係唔想有咁多人同車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eadc32db47480a66547c7e90d3bfadd42fed3889","tid":734582,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T17:54:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8055eb5600dd89d35a49e28286b383e7868373f","tid":734582,"uid":13882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eadc32db47480a66547c7e90d3bfadd42fed3889","tid":734582,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T17:54:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T18:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唉，真係好逼"}]}